char_1118_02_24","textHome":"月夜去买果汁的时候，我在这里看着。@把行李留在沙滩上是很不安全的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":111802}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":111802,"motion":300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_25","textHome":"好！早饭也好好吃了，精神满满，@玩的话就算天热也没有关系哦。@那么，带上水……出发吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":111802,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_26","textHome":"月夜好像有些疲倦，@午饭给她做了杏鲍菇肉卷。@还有一些剩的，要吃么？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111800,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voice":"vo_char_1118_00_02","textHome":"双胞胎的妹妹，天音月咲和——@双胞胎的姐姐天音月夜。@您和我们两人同时见面还是第一次呢。@对吧，过会儿和我们一起去游泳吧！"},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_00_02","textHome":"双胞胎的妹妹，天音月咲和——@双胞胎的姐姐天音月夜。@您和我们两人同时见面还是第一次呢。@对吧，过会儿和我们一起去游泳吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":111802,"lipSynch":0},{"id":111800,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":111800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":111800,"lipSynch":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_27","textHome":"呜……月夜还没到吗？@烟花大会就要开始了……肚子也饿了……@稍微去看看路边摊吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"id":111802,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":1}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_28","textHome":"夜晚的海，黑得像是要把人吸进去一样，@虽然有点害怕，但是当月光一下子@照上去的时候……特别漂亮呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":111802,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_29","textHome":"我很擅长游泳的哦！@体育课得时候也拿出了好成绩，@游泳部也邀请了我很多次……@啊？你不信么？@那样的话……现在一起游一下？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":111802,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_30","textHome":"人多的场所容易出现魔女的话……@这个海水浴场也不例外。@为了不让快乐时间被打扰，@必须做好警戒呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":111802,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":111802,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_31","textHome":"那个，我们有换衣服的时间么？@虽然去无尽镜界没关系，@但是不想就这样穿着重要的泳衣去……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"id":111802,"motion":300}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_02_32","textHome":"真是的，没听说海水浴场这么挤啊！@海之家也满员